{"tid":133853,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"送禮幾多錢最好？銅記情侶咁樣講","createTime":"2017-02-25T04:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T04:00:19.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b3ee2cb9bba68ab144b2cbdda895ee31a4fabb7","tid":133853,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T04:00:19.000Z","msg":"一年一度的情人節相相信令不少情侶（或非情侶）痛苦萬分。其中一個來自地獄的考驗，想必是「到底買甚麼給對方？」還有「要買多少錢的禮物？」婚禮人情有海鮮價，記者相信情人節禮物也必如是，所以獨自闖入情侶雲集的銅鑼灣，看看大家的選擇。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170208/large/618ss01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170208%2Flarge%2F618ss01.jpg&h=f533ede1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n右邊美女沒有男朋友，男士們，加把勁吧！<br />\n<br />\n首先將價錢定為0元、1元至100元、100元至500元、500元至1000元，以及1,000元以上。令記者大感驚訝的是，不少人今年都表示不會送禮，尤其是女生，有10人在選擇0元，「沒有情人」、「結了婚」是她們的理由。<br />\n<br />\n而只有一個年輕男子選擇送1元至100元的禮物，他指因為自己是學生，未能負擔太貴的價錢。最多人選擇100元至500元，選擇500元至1000元的人也不少，估計是最可負擔的價錢。而1,000元以上的送禮選擇也不少，大路如頸鏈、錶、耳環等，也有男士說會用1,000元送花，或者送出自己的心，即是無價，嘩，個心真的馬上離一離。<br />\n<br />\n不過，以上數據只供參考，記者聽得最多的一句還是「看看他/她的表現吧」。之不過，就算沒有物質，也有很多傳達愛的方法，大家不必拘泥於禮物吧。<br />\n<br />\n記者：胡可欣<br />\n攝影：鄧鴻欣<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170208/large/618ss02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170208%2Flarge%2F618ss02.jpg&h=7bbcea02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多得記者提醒，這位先生才記起情人節快到。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170208/large/618ss03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170208%2Flarge%2F618ss03.jpg&h=b716ea9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左邊男士指自己會送1,000元以上的花給對方，嘩嘩。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170208/large/618ss04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170208%2Flarge%2F618ss04.jpg&h=bdd3e385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n右邊女士指結了婚不會慶祝情人節，會慶祝結婚周年，其實結了婚一樣可以是情人呢。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/special/art/20170208/19920986\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fspecial%2Fart%2F20170208%2F19920986&d=7LXG2TbyL57SoPLQ%2FF4DpSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c26d20df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fspecial%2Fart%2F20170208%2F19920986&h=04e6ee32\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/special/art/20170208/19920986</a>"}]}